msgid "Documenting a full proposal"
msgstr "Redactar una propuesta completa"

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:23
msgid "This course is designed for BID programme applicants who have advanced to the full proposal phase."
msgstr "Este curso está dirigido a los solicitantes del programa BID que hayan pasado a la fase de presentación de la propuesta completa."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:30
msgid "A BID programme project advanced to the full proposal phase."
msgstr "Un proyecto del programa BID avanzó a la fase de propuesta completa."

#. type: delimited block =
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:31
msgid "Individuals completing this course should have a good command of English. While efforts are made to provide materials in other languages, instruction/videos will be in English."
msgstr "Para completar este curso, se requiere un buen dominio del inglés. Si bien se procura ofrecer materiales en otros idiomas, las instrucciones y los videos serán en inglés."

#. type: Plain text
#: en/project-planning/modules/ROOT/pages/description.adoc:35
msgid "If you need to learn more about GBIF in advance of the course, it is recommended to complete the https://docs.gbif.org/course-introduction-to-gbif[Introduction to GBIF course^]."
msgstr ""

